                  <rs id="t18660507-464-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18660507-464-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18660507-464-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>, Feloniously forging and uttering a receipt for 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 4½<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. with intent to defraud.</rs>
